# Targeting LLM (optional). With NO key set, the app uses a deterministic mock
# seeded from sample data — always demoable. Set a key to use a real model.
#
# Provider-agnostic: works with any OpenAI-compatible endpoint (Groq, OpenRouter,
# Together, etc. — all have free tiers). Server-side only; never exposed to the
# browser. The model only ever receives surviving channel names + the free-text
# brief — never a budget.

LLM_API_KEY=
# LLM_BASE_URL=https://api.groq.com/openai/v1
# LLM_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile

# Ad-image generation (optional). With NO key, ad mockups use the client's own
# hero image (from their website) or a branded gradient. Set a key to synthesise
# an objective-aware background via any OpenAI-compatible images endpoint.
# IMAGE_API_KEY=
# IMAGE_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1
# IMAGE_MODEL=gpt-image-1
